<b>TOTAL on the World Wide Web - why? </b><p>


TOTAL is one of the world's leading international oil and gas companies and a dynamic <br>player in specialty chemicals.<p>

Why did we create this site? Because our Group is present in over one hundred countries, because our operations span the globe, and because we have shareholders, partners and customers around the world. And above all, because Internet now offers this new medium to communicate with you.<p>

What is our aim ? To let you get to know us and our Group better. Not only through our products, but by sharing our achievements and goals, by exploring our industrial and geographic diversity, and by participating in the way we at TOTAL think and work.<p>

